<div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
  <h1>🪑 Tesla Interior Guides</h1>
  <p>Door handles, speaker upgrades, seat fixes, trim repairs, and interior modifications. Everything you need to maintain and upgrade your Tesla's cabin.</p>
